@dy3p8ntrkid wrote:

All 3 are very easy yes. Login as a starter search the coords of the location and find the area, then when you find it which is probly in testworldloader or w/e I haven’t used 317’s in forever.

  1. if you are changing ::home to ::skill just get the coords of where you want to go and switch them with the one on ::home or w/e or if ur making another teleport copy ::home’s command and put it right below ::home. Then just replace the coords for the duplicated command with the ones you wanna go to… Find coords most likely by typing ::coords

  2. For a teleport entered in a quest tab just search the name and replace it with what you want.

I haven’t used 317’s in forever if some don’t work then my fault lol, but good luck.
